title: He Cant Out Cheat Me
itunes:title: He Cant Out Cheat Me
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, my boyfriend and I are 44 years old and we have been together for years. I lost count on how long we’ve actually been a couple because we were roommates first, then we started fooling around, then we stopped seeing other people since we were living together. We became a couple after our family and friends considered us a couple.......................................
